Yawan cututtukan da ke ci gaba da saurin yaduwa na cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, yana tabbatar da cewa ko da yake yana cikin wani mataki daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da UTIs ya kamata su ƙara shirya don ɓarkewar marasa lafiya da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawa, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an samu rahoton wasu masu cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san asalin su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ne, wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus 2 mai saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da aka samu har zuwa yanzu ita ce kashi 80 cikin ɗari na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna kamuwa da cutar mai sauƙi, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin su suna murmurewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari na masu cutar, COVID-19 ta ci gaba zuwa wani mummunan ciwo, wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari na masu cutar suka ci gaba zuwa mummunan ciwo, wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Ingila kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a yanzu a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta bazu a wurare daban-daban, kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya yanzu haka yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an riga an gano cututtukan COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Ingila, kuma tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da ranar da aka ambata a sama, an ba da rahoton mutane 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun jimlar lambobi da kuma yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga kafofin hukuma kawai, kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin ƙididdigar yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19, mun ƙididdige yawan adadin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 da aka yanke, don haka muna la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Ingila a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna jimlar adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa har zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8 na safe, kuma mun kwatanta da na Italiya na lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila
Yanayin da ake samu na kwanaki 14 na yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila gabaɗaya ya bi na lardin Hubei na China (Hoto na 1).
Gabaɗaya, ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya, yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya faru ne musamman saboda saurin karuwar shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a cikin yawan COVID-19 (abubuwan haɓaka).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila idan aka kwatanta da Italiya na lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya ce, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8 na safe, wasu kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun riga sun bayar da rahoton adadin adadin masu cutar kamar na Italiya makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna karuwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da Ingila.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin yawan cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a ayyukan tsarin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma wataƙila ma'anar shari'o'i daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda za a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwaji don sabuntawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan asibiti da/ko ICU na COVID-19 a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Ya kamata, duk da haka, a tattara su a cikin tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu tare da mai da hankali kan yawan lambobin da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani binciken da aka gudanar tsakanin 2010 da 2011 ya nuna bambancin bambancin da ke tsakanin wadatar ICU da kuma gadajen marasa lafiya a Turai, daga gadaje 29,2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4,2 a Portugal a kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 ICU da gadaje na kulawa mai tsanani don yawan jama'a 100,000 tsakanin 2010 da 2011).
An samar da yanayin samfurin da ya shafi cikawar tsarin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Ingila na yawan asibitocin COVID-19 da ke da haɗarin fiye da kashi 90% na ƙarfin gadaje masu kulawa mai tsanani, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC Rapid Risk Assessment on COVID-19.
Ganin cewa har yanzu an tattara lokuta a wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa galibi suna kula da ƙayyadadden yanki na yanki, ya kamata a ba da fifiko ga samar da bayanai game da lokuta da gadajen kulawa da gaggawa a cikin Ƙididdigar Ƙungiyoyin Ƙasa don Bayanai 2 (NUTS-2).
Misalin Italiya da kuma yanayin da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da UTIs dole ne su shirya don yanayin ci gaba da yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda yake a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin saurin kimanta haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, mai saurin aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanyar hanawa zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda saurin ƙaruwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in da aka yi hasashen zai iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita ayyukan su yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da su ba.
Har ila yau, ƙididdigar haɗarin gaggawa ta lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara ƙoƙarin hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba su yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya samun ƙarin marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
