Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a fadin kasar da kuma kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da sama da mutane 80,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19, tare da sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 da suka warke kuma sama da marasa lafiya 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "maƙiyi na farko na jama'a" ne, kuma yana da iko fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19, gami da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ganewar asali da magani, tun lokacin da aka fara bayar da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya ƙaddara jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan talifin yana so ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a wannan sabon yanki mai saurin ci gaba.
A duk lokacin da ya dace, za mu kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wata cuta da CoV ke haifarwa, wato Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, annobar shekara ta 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da kuma yadda za a magance cutar da kuma wasu batutuwa masu muhimmanci.
CoVs an ɗauka a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta marasa mutuwa ga mutane, galibi suna haifar da kusan 15% na sanyi.
Amma a wannan karni, mun sami sau biyu na cutar CoVs masu cutarwa ga mutane, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da annobar da ta samo asali daga China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annobar CoV ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Fig. Fig.1,1, an fara ba da rahoton wasu cututtukan cututtukan huhu da ba a san asalin su ba a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an buga jerin kwayoyin cutar CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, an ba da rahoton farkon mutuwar Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa birane, larduna da ƙasashe maƙwabta.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an sanar da cewa ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun kamu da cutar, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa ana iya samun kamuwa da cutar tsakanin mutane.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan, kuma an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken asibiti na farko game da cutar ya ba da rahoton cewa daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da ke da tabbacin shari'ar 21 ne kawai suka taɓa tuntuɓar kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan, wanda aka ɗauka cewa asalin asalin dabba ne ya fara kamuwa da cutar.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
