Ana iya raba su zuwa jinsuna huɗu, wato: alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, waɗanda aka san cewa alpha coronaviruses da beta coronaviruses suna cutar da mutane.
Glycoprotein spike (S) na envelope yana haɗuwa da masu karɓar ƙwayoyin salula na enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 (ECA2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, kuma a cikin jerin, haɗuwa da membrane yana faruwa.
Ana sakin kwayoyin RNA na kwayar cutar a cikin kwayar halitta; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta kwayar halitta, RNA na genomic tare da glycoproteins da aka rufe da kuma nucleocapsid sunadaran suna samar da vesicles wanda ke dauke da virins, wanda ke haɗuwa da membrane plasma kuma ya saki kwayar cutar.
An fara rahoton jerin kwayoyin halittar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
An gano SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon nau'in betacoronavirus tare da sama da kashi 99.98 cikin ɗari na asalin kwayoyin halitta tsakanin samfuran 10 da aka tattara daga wurin da cutar ta fara, Kasuwar 'Ya'yan Ruwan Huanan a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da SARS-CoV fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar amfani da na'urar daukar hotan takardu, an gano kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙananan sassan ƙwayoyin cuta na iska.
An gano cewa ECA2 na mutum mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 ne, da SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da furotin ECA2 na ɗan adam cikin rauni fiye da furotin na SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a cikin marasa lafiya fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 kuma na iya samar da sabon ƙaramin furotin wanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf3b da furotin da aka ɓoye wanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 orf3b na iya taka rawa a cikin cutar kwayar cuta da hana bayyanar IFNβ; duk da haka, orf8 ba ta da wani yanki ko dalili na aiki.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al., ya ba da rahoton tsarin cryo-EM na ECA2 na ɗan adam mai tsayi duka zuwa ƙudurin 2,9 Å a cikin hadadden tare da jigilar amino acid B0AT1.
An gano cewa hadaddun, wanda ke da buɗe da rufe ƙira, an haɗa shi kamar dimer, kuma hadaddun ECA2-B0AT1 na iya haɗa sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke ba da shaida don ganewa da kamuwa da cutar CoV.
B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin magani don tantance magunguna don kawar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
