Gabaɗaya, bayan kwayar cuta ta mamaye mai masaukin, tsarin garkuwar jiki na asali na mai masaukin ya fara gane ta ta hanyar masu karɓar karɓar ƙirar (PRRs), gami da masu karɓar lectin na nau'in C, mai karɓar nau'in Toll (TLR), mai karɓar nau'in NOD (NLR) da mai karɓar nau'in RIG-I (RLR).
Ta hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar tana haifar da bayyanar abubuwan kumburi, balaga na ƙwayoyin dendritic da kuma samar da nau'in interferons na I (IFNs), wanda ke iyakance yaduwar kwayar cutar da kuma hanzarta phagocytosis na macrophages na kwayar cutar.
Amma, furotin N na SARS-CoV zai iya taimaka wa kwayar cutar ta tsere daga amsawar rigakafi.
Ba da daɗewa ba, tsarin garkuwar jiki zai soma yaƙi da ƙwayar.
Kwayoyin T, ciki har da CD4+ da CD8+ T cells suna taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kariya.
Kwayoyin CD4+ T suna motsa ƙwayoyin B don samar da ƙwayoyin rigakafi na musamman ga kwayar cutar, kuma ƙwayoyin CD8+ T suna kashe ƙwayoyin cutar kai tsaye.
Kwayoyin T masu taimakawa suna samar da kwayoyin cytokines masu taimakawa wajen kare kwayoyin.
Koyaya, CoV na iya hana ayyukan T-cell ta hanyar haifar da apoptosis na T-cell.
Tsarin rigakafi na humoral, gami da kari kamar su C3a da C5a, ma yana da mahimmanci don yaƙar kamuwa da kwayar cuta.
Alal misali, ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga mai haƙuri da ya warke sun kawar da MERS-CoV.
