Shin za a ƙara kwana 24 a keɓewar?
Zazzabi yawanci shine farkon kuma babban alamar COVID-19, wanda zai iya zuwa shi kaɗai ko tare da wasu alamun, kamar bushewar tari, numfashi, ciwon tsoka, zazzaɓi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, zazzaɓi, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami dyspnea da/ ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan bayyanar cututtukan cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, marasa lafiya sun ci gaba da sauri zuwa cututtukan numfashi, damuwa, acidosis na metabolism da clotopathy.
Marasa lafiya da zazzabi da/ko cututtukan numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, koda ba su da wata cuta a cikin binciken hoto na huhu, ya kamata a tantance su don cutar don samun ganewar asali.
Wani binciken alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98 cikin ɗari na alamun cutar sun kasance zazzabi, kashi 76 cikin ɗari na tari mai bushe, kashi 55 cikin ɗari na dyspnea, da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na zawo; kashi 8 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya sun buƙaci tallafin numfashi.
An bayar da rahoton irin wannan sakamakon a cikin binciken biyu na kwanan nan na ƙungiyar iyali da ƙungiyar da ke da watsawa daga mutum mara alama.
A kwatankwacin haka, binciken alƙaluma a cikin 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiyar MERS-CoV suma suna da zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushewa (47%) da dyspnea (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun.
Koyaya, kashi 80% na marasa lafiya sun buƙaci tallafin numfashi, fiye da marasa lafiyar COVID-19, wanda ya ƙunshi mafi yawan mutuwar MERS idan aka kwatanta da COVID-19.
Diarrhea (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) an kuma lura dasu a cikin marasa lafiya tare da MERS.
