Koyaya, akwai manyan bambance-bambance tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda ke da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar cutar da kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma maza fiye da mata, kuma tsananin cutar da yawan mutuwa ma sun fi girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
