Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙarancin ƙarfi, masu ƙarancin ƙarfi, da RNA mai sauƙi.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta, tsakanin kilobases 26 zuwa 32, a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA an kira su "CoVs" saboda siffar kambi lokacin da aka lura da su a cikin madubin lantarki.
Game da tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba a rarraba su ba waɗanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu cikin uku na kwayoyin halitta suna dauke da tsarin karatun budewa guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), wanda aka fassara a cikin pp1a da pp1ab polyproteins.
Ana sake canza polyproteins kuma suna samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, wanda aka kira nsp1 zuwa nsp16.
Sauran sashin kwayoyin halitta yana dauke da ORFs don sunadarai na tsarin, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙayyadaddun ƙwayoyin cuta suna ƙunshe da ƙwayoyin CoV daban-daban.
Bisa ga bambanci a cikin jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu (alphaCoV, betaCoV, gammaCoV, da deltaCoV), daga cikinsu jinsi betaCoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba shi zuwa layi huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar ilimin halitta ta nuna cewa jemage da rodents suna ba da tushen kwayoyin halitta ga yawancin alphaCoVs da betaCoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban taskar gammaCoVs da deltaCoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare iyakokin jinsuna, kuma wasu sun zama manyan cututtukan ɗan adam.
A halin yanzu, an san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da cutar korona (HCoVs).
Daga cikin su, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alphaCoVs.
Sauran betaCoVs biyar sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2.
Kwayoyin cutar HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 galibi suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya kamar sanyi da / ko zawo.
A akasin wannan, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 suna da cutar cuta sosai kuma suna haifar da mummunan kamuwa da cututtukan ƙananan numfashi a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya, tare da babban damar ci gaban cutar rashin jin daɗin numfashi (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtuka.
An ware HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga jikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar cikakken nazarin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun suna haifar da alamun ƙuntatawa.
A gaskiya ma, ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da HCoVs ba shi da lahani har zuwa barkewar cutar SARS.
Cutar SARS da ta ɓarke a shekara ta 2003 tana ɗaya daga cikin cututtuka mafi muni a tarihinmu, ta harba mutane fiye da 8,000, kuma yawan mutanen da suka mutu a sakamakon cutar ya kai kusan kashi 10.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar murar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta zama wata annoba mai ci a yankin Larabawa, kuma ta bazu a wasu wurare a duniya.
Sabuwar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wacce daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce mai haifar da annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe rayuka sama da 3,120 kuma ta harba mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
