Tashin SARS-CoV-2 ya bi ka'idodin da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suka samo asali.
Yayin da aka gano cewa betaCoV na jemage yana da kashi 95% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV, akwai CoV na jemage wanda ke da kashi 96% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Ko da yake an gano cewa civets da sauran dabbobi a kasuwanni suna dauke da ƙwayoyin cuta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV, ba a gano matsakaitan runduna don SARS-CoV-2 ba.
An gano betaCoVs daga pangolins, tare da babban kamannin SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa pangolins na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin masu karɓar baƙi, ko kuma pangolin betaCoVs na iya ba da gudummawar ɓangarorin kwayoyin halitta don sigar ƙarshe ta SARS-CoV-2.
Ko da yake tambayoyi sun rage, babu wata hujja da ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 mutum ne ya samar da shi ba da gangan ba.
CoVs sun sake dawowa cikin hankalin duniya saboda barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 kwanan nan.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin jemage da sauran dabbobi ya canza ra'ayinmu game da mahimmancin asalin dabbobi da kuma wuraren adana HCoVs a cikin watsa tsakanin mutane.
Shaida mai yawa ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2 sun samo asali ne daga jemage kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar masu watsawa.
Tun da yake kamuwa da SARS-CoV ya samo asali ne daga hulɗar mutane da civets a kasuwanni, rufe kasuwannin ruwa da kashe civets a waɗannan kasuwanni na iya kawo ƙarshen annobar SARS.
A cikin wannan tunani, ya kamata a cire pangolins daga kasuwannin da ke da danshi don hana yaduwar cutar ta dabbobi, saboda gano yawancin layin betaCoVs na pangolin da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Koyaya, har yanzu ba a bayyana ba a cikin nazarin gaba ko SARS-CoV-2 yana yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa, da kuma yadda ake yaduwar.
A gefe guda kuma, MERS-CoV ya daɗe yana cikin dabbobi masu kama da rakumi.
Waɗannan raƙuman suna da muhimmanci wajen sufuri, kuma suna ba da nama, madara, fata, da ulu ga mutanen yankin.
An rarraba su sosai a Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka, ba zai yiwu a kashe dukan raƙuma don a shawo kan MERS ba, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwannin dabbobi a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da sake barkewar cutar MERS, ya kamata a ɗauki cikakkiyar hanyar haɓaka alluran rigakafin MERS-CoV masu tasiri ga raƙuma, a hade tare da sauran matakan kula da kamuwa da cuta.
Idan ba mu iya kawar da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba, za su iya haifar da sabon ƙwayoyin cuta.
Akwai wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da dabbobi da ke yawo a cikin yanayi.
Musamman, CoVs na jemage tare da yiwuwar cutar dabbobi sun bambanta sosai.
Akwai dama da yawa cewa waɗannan CoVs na dabbobi zasu iya haɓaka da sake haɗuwa, wanda zai haifar da fitowar sababbin CoVs waɗanda ke da saurin yaduwa da / ko kisa ga mutane a nan gaba.
Dole ne a daina al'adar cin namun daji a wasu wurare a kasar Sin don rage hulɗar da ba dole ba tsakanin mutane da dabbobi.
Tare da rikicin SARS, MERS da COVID-19, za a buƙaci ingantaccen shirin amsawa da shiri.
A gaskiya, akwai ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa da suka daɗe suna wanzuwa a duniya.
Suna zama a cikin tafkunan su na halitta har sai akwai damar ƙaura zuwa wata halitta.
Ko da yake jemage suna da halaye da yawa da ke sa su iya yaɗa cutar, amma za a iya rage haɗarin mutane su kamu da jemage da kuma wasu dabbobin daji idan aka koya wa mutane su guji su.
Ana buƙatar ci gaba da sa ido a cikin dabbobi masu shayarwa don samun kyakkyawar fahimta game da yanayin halittu na CoVs da kuma rundunansu na halitta, wanda zai taimaka wajen hana watsawa daga dabbobi zuwa mutane da kuma barkewar annoba a nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar ƙwayoyin cuta ita ce mutane su guji wuraren da ƙwayoyin cuta ke ɓoyewa.
Har yanzu akwai wasu abubuwa da ba a gano ba game da asalin SARS-CoV-2 daga dabbobi.
Na farko, idan jemage suna watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa pangolins, yana da mahimmanci a gano a wane yanayi jemage da pangolins zasu iya raba wuri ɗaya.
Na biyu, idan jemage suna taka rawa kai tsaye wajen watsawa ga mutane, ya kamata a tantance yadda mutane ke hulɗa da jemage.
Na uku, idan dabba ta uku tana da matsayin mai karɓar bakuncin na gaskiya, dole ne a bayyana yadda yake hulɗa da nau'ikan halittu daban-daban, gami da mutane, jemage da pangolins.
A ƙarshe, tunda dabbobi masu shayarwa da yawa, gami da dabbobin gida, na iya zama masu saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, yakamata a gudanar da sa ido da kamuwa da gwaji.
Idan jemage ne, pangolin ko wani dabba mai shayarwa, ana sa ran za a gano SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma kwayoyin iyayensa da suka yi kama da juna a cikin masu karɓar su a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a wannan fannin zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da mahimman bayanai game da rigakafi da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Wajibi ne a sabunta ka'idojin ganewar asali na "wanda ake zargi" da "wanda aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19".
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar saurin jagora don ganewa da kula da kamuwa da cutar 2019 (2019-nCoV) ta sabuwar coronavirus. Wannan jagorar tana ba da kwarewarmu kuma tana da kyau ga magance wannan annoba ta duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwa ce. Fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga ci gaba da binciken bincike da gogewa a cikin aikin asibiti; saboda wannan, hanyoyin bincike da magani suma ana sabunta su koyaushe.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wani bayani game da jagorarmu kuma mun ba da sababbin ka'idodin ganewar asali na "al'amarin da ake zargi" da "al'amarin da aka tabbatar" bisa ga sabon Jagoran Gano da Kula da COVID-19 (siffa ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiyar Jama'ar Sin ya buga.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu ake kira cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), kuma ana kiran kwayar cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai tsanani 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta rarraba COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don magance kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta tsara jagorar jagora mai sauri da aka buga akan layi a cikin Binciken Likita na Soja a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Ya jawo hankali sosai tun lokacin da aka buga shi.
Koyaya, lura cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce. Fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga ci gaba da binciken bincike da gogewa a cikin aikin asibiti; saboda wannan, hanyoyin bincike da magani suma ana sabunta su koyaushe.
Alal misali, Jagoran Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya wallafa tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020 ya ƙunshi jimillar bugu bakwai tare da canje-canje masu yawa a cikin wasu.
Jagorarmu ta karɓi bayani daga Zhou et al., wanda ya ba da shawara mai sauƙi bisa ga kwarewar asibiti.
Wannan aikin ya ƙara sabon shaida ga jagorarmu kuma ya ba da mahimman bayanai game da wannan annobar ta duniya.
Mun amince da aikin da suke yi kuma mun nuna godiya.
Koyaya, aikin su yana buƙatar sabuntawa daidai da sabon Jagoran Ganowa da Kula da COVID-19 (siffa ta bakwai na gwaji) da kuma binciken kwanan nan.
A cewar bugu na bakwai (3 ga Maris 2020), don tabbatar da yanayin da ake zargi, ya zama dole a haɗa ɗayan abubuwan tarihin cututtukan cuta tare da abubuwa biyu na bayyanar cututtuka don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma abubuwa uku na bayyanar cututtuka suna buƙatar cika idan babu bayyanar cututtuka:
Tarihin cututtuka: (1) tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewaye ko a wasu al'ummomin da aka samu rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) tarihin tuntuɓar masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (wanda gwajin nucleic acid ya nuna tabbatacce); (3) tarihin tuntuɓar marasa lafiya da zazzabi ko cututtukan numfashi daga Wuhan da kewaye ko daga wasu al'ummomin da aka samu rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) tarihin tuntuɓar rukuni na mutane da aka tabbatar da cutar (fiye da ko daidai da mutane biyu da zazzabi da/ko cututtukan numfashi a cikin makonni 2 a cikin ƙananan wurare kamar gida, ofis, aji, da sauransu).
Bayyanar asibiti: (1) zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi; (2) tare da damar gano hoto na kamuwa da COVID-19; (3) yawan adadin farin jini yana nuna al'ada, rage ko rage ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin lymphocytes a farkon farkon bayyanar cututtuka.
Gano tabbataccen yanayin ya kamata ya dogara ne akan yanayin da ake zargi da kowane ɗayan waɗannan abubuwa masu zuwa na serological ko pathogenic: (1) gwajin PCR mai kyau don SARS-CoV-2; (2) cikakken tsarin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar wanda ke nuna babban daidaito game da sabbin cututtukan coronavirus da aka sani; (3) tabbatacce ga ƙwayoyin cuta na IgM da IgG na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin ƙwayar cuta; ko wani canji na ƙwayoyin cuta na IgG na SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa tabbatacce ko ƙaruwa a cikin taken sama da sau huɗu a lokacin murmurewa sama da na lokacin matsananci.
Za mu iya lura cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na ainihi don nucleic acid a cikin jini ko samfurin numfashi a bugu na biyu da na uku (daga 18 da 22 ga Janairu, 2020, bi da bi).
An ƙara gano cututtukan cututtukan jini a bugu na huɗu da na biyar (daga Janairu 27, 2020 da Fabrairu 8, 2020, bi da bi), kuma an ƙara shaidar serological a bugu na bakwai.
Waɗannan canje-canjen sun dogara ne akan ci gaba da aikin masu bincike don neman mafi kyawun kayan aikin gano nucleic acid don saurin ganewa da kuma samfurori na numfashi, gami da ɗaukar jini, wanda ya haɓaka wadatar samfuran daban-daban kuma ya taimaka wajen kawo sakamako mai kyau na ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman ga ƙa'idodin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin shaida da ke tunatar da mu mu mai da hankali ga marasa lafiya masu alamun cututtuka da marasa alamun cututtuka.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a sabunta tsarin Zhou et al. saboda ya sanya mutum ba tare da alamun asibiti a matsayin "mai hadari ba".
Hakanan ana buƙatar tabbatar da tsarin ƙididdigar a cikin ƙarin bincike da ayyukan asibiti.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin hujjoji na kai tsaye sun fito kuma muna roƙon masu karatu su ba da ra'ayoyinsu.
Don ganewar asali na "wanda ake zargi" da "wanda aka tabbatar da shi", muna ba da shawarar cewa ku bincika kuma ku bi sababbin jagororin ƙasarku.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta kuma sabunta jagorarmu a kan lokaci don taimaka muku.
Bangladesh ta samu karin mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19, mafi yawan mutane a kowace rana
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da sabbin mutuwar mutane biyar sakamakon COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana guda sakamakon cutar.
A ranar jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, Kula da Cututtuka da Bincike ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton cewa adadin mutanen da aka tabbatar da su sun haɗa da masu cutar 114 da kuma 33 da suka warke da ke gida.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17.
A wani rahoto da aka wallafa a yanar gizo, darektan hukumar IEDCR, Dakta Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
Dokta Meerjady ta ce, mutane biyu sun fi shekara 60, biyu kuma suna tsakanin shekara 51 da 60, ɗaya kuma yana tsakanin shekara 41 da 50.
Ta kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe daga Dhaka ne.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya shaida wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Anadolu Agency cewa daya daga cikin wadanda aka kashe shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, darektan hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengali, wanda aka yi wa jinya a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A ranar Asabar, a cikin wata sanarwa ta bidiyo ta yanar gizo, Ministan sufuri na hanyoyi da gadoji na Bengal Obaidul Quader ya ce za a dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka tsara tun farko, har zuwa ranar Asabar mai zuwa.
Wannan dakatarwar zirga-zirgar jama'a ta fara ne a ranar 26 ga Maris kuma an shirya ta ƙare a ranar Asabar, 4 ga Afrilu.
Har yanzu ana ba da izinin jigilar kayayyaki masu mahimmanci (kayan magani, mai da abinci).
An fara samun mutane da suka kamu da COVID-19 a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga Maris, a cikin mutane biyu da suka dawo daga Italiya da kuma matar ɗaya daga cikinsu.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, dukan ukun sun warke.
SARS-CoV-2 ya wuce kamuwa da cutar miliyan a duniya
