Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana cewa barkewar cutar COVID-19  cutar da kwayar cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ke haifarwa a halin yanzu annoba ce.
Ko da yake kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu ne kawai, ba yadda hatsarin ke ba, WHO ta nanata bukatar sa gwamnatoci su ɗauki mataki:
Duk ƙasashe na iya canza yanayin wannan annoba.
Idan kasashe za su iya ganowa, gwadawa, magance, warewa, bin diddigin mutane da kuma tattara jama'a don amsawa, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna matukar damuwa game da yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma yadda ta zama ruwan dare gama gari da kuma rashin aiki.
Dokta Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, ya ce wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
A wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce "ban da mura, ba a lura da wata kwayar cutar numfashi ba tun lokacin da ta fara zuwa ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annoba da cutar coronavirus ta fara ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin annoba da za a iya sarrafa ta ba a lokaci guda".
Sabon matsayin annobar ya biyo bayan shawarar da WHO ta yanke a watan Janairu na ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a da ke da damuwa a duniya.
Darakta na Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Ƙasa ta Amirka, Dokta Anthony Fauci, ya ce wannan annoba "za ta ƙara muni".
A ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar sama da 4,600.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 201920 annobar cutar annobar cutar coronavirus ce ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce cutar coronavirus mai saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi mai tsanani 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ke haifarwa.
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a ta duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020 kuma an gane ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Har zuwa 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a ƙasashe 210 da yankuna, tare da mutuwar mutane 97,000.
Mutane kusan 364,000 sun warke.
