A ranar 20 ga Janairun 2020, an tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu.
Hukumar kiwon lafiya ta kasar ta ba da rahoton wani babban ci gaba a cikin shari'o'in da aka tabbatar a ranar 20 ga Fabrairu, wanda galibi ana danganta shi ne ga wani taro a Daegu na wani sabon motsi na addini, wanda aka sani da Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Ana zargin cewa masu ibada na Shincheonji da suka ziyarci Daegu daga Wuhan ne suka haifar da barkewar cutar.
