An kuma yi tasiri da sauya jadawalin jiragen sama. Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar da abin da aka ɗauka mafi girma kuma mafi kyawun tsari a duniya dangane da tantance yawan mutane don cutar. Ƙasar ta kuma ware mutanen da ke da cutar kuma ta bi da kuma keɓe waɗanda suka taɓa saduwa da su.
Hanyoyin tantancewa sun haɗa da buƙatar rahoton mutum na alamun bayyanar cututtuka ga waɗanda suka zo daga balaguron ƙasa da ƙasa ta hanyar aikace-aikacen wayar hannu, gwajin kwayar cutar ta hanyar tuki, tare da sakamakon da ke samuwa a rana mai zuwa, ban da haɓaka ƙarfin gwaji, wanda ya ba da damar gwada mutane 20,000 kowace rana.
An yi la'akari da shirin Koriya ta Kudu a matsayin nasara wajen sarrafa barkewar cutar, kodayake ba ta sanya birane gaba ɗaya cikin keɓewa ba.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun neman tsige Moon bisa zargin rashin kulawar gwamnati da barkewar cutar, ko kuma suna yabon yadda ya amsa.
A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa Koriya ta Kudu ta sami mafi ƙarancin adadin masu cutar a cikin makonni huɗu.
A ranar 29 ga Maris an sanar da cewa daga ranar 1 ga Afrilu duk sabbin masu shigowa daga kasashen waje dole ne su shiga keɓewa na makonni biyu.
Ta hanyar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 1 ga Afrilu, Koriya ta Kudu ta sami buƙatun taimako don gwajin cutar daga ƙasashe daban-daban 121.
Iran ta tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu a Qom, inda, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita, mutane biyu suka mutu a ranar.
Matakan farko da gwamnatin ta sanar sun hada da soke kide kide da sauran al'adu, wasanni, da kuma taron addini a ranakun Juma'a, rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi, da makarantu.
Iran ta samu Rials biliyan biyar don magance cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairun 2020 cewa ba shi da wani shiri game da wuraren da ke cikin keɓewa da cutar ta shafa, kuma za a sanya mutane a keɓewa kawai.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren iyakance tafiye-tafiye tsakanin biranen a watan Maris, kodayake zirga-zirgar ababen hawa tsakanin biranen kafin Sabuwar Shekarar Fasha Nowruz ta ci gaba.
Wuraren ibada na Shi'a a Qom sun kasance a bude ga mahajjata har zuwa 16 ga Maris, 2020.
A yayin da ake zargin cewa an rufe yaduwar cutar a Iran, sama da kasashe goma sun sake gano cututtukansu da suka shafi Iran a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu suna nuna cewa yaduwar cutar na iya zama mafi muni fiye da 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito har zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, tare da 23 daga cikin mambobi 290 da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta yi kira ga hukumomin kurkuku na Iran da su saki masu kare hakkin dan adam da aka tsare saboda rashin amincewarsu da zaman lafiya ba tare da wata doka ba, da kuma sakin duk fursunonin da suka cancanci.
Hukumar ta ce akwai hadarin yaduwar cutar a cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin tsare mutane, wadanda kuma ke fama da rashin kulawar likita.
