Akalla 'yan siyasa 12 da suka yi ritaya da jami'an gwamnati sun mutu sakamakon cutar har zuwa ranar 17 ga Maris.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, Iran tana da sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa da kuma mutuwa guda a kowane minti goma sakamakon cutar Coronavirus.
A cewar wani wakilin Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, akwai adadin mutane da suka kamu da cutar a Iran fiye da sau biyar.
An ba da shawarar cewa takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya wa Iran na iya shafar ikon kuɗin ƙasar don amsa cutar kwayar cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan 'Yancin Dan Adam ya nemi a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
