Ana iya amfani da su don gano kamuwa da cuta a cikin mutane da suka fara kwanaki 7 ko jim kaɗan bayan bayyanar cututtuka, don ƙayyade rigakafi, da kuma lura da yawan jama'a. Ana iya yin gwaje-gwaje a cikin cibiyoyin bincike na tsakiya (CLT) ko ta hanyar gwaje-gwajen gwaje-gwaje na nesa (PoCT).
Tsarin sarrafa kansa mai inganci a yawancin dakunan gwaje-gwaje na asibiti zai iya yin waɗannan gwaje-gwajen, amma kasancewarsu zai dogara da yawan samar da kowane tsarin.
Don CLT, ana amfani da samfurin jini guda ɗaya, kodayake ana iya amfani da samfurori da yawa don bin tsarin rigakafi.
Don PoCT, ana yawan samun samfurin jini guda ɗaya ta hanyar bugun jini.
