Ciwon amai da gudawa da kuma ciwon huhu suna kashe yara kusan miliyan 3.5 kowace shekara.
A cewar UNICEF, wanke hannu da sabulu kafin cin abinci da kuma bayan yin wanka zai iya ceton rayuka fiye da allurar rigakafi ko kuma maganin likita, yana rage mutuwar masu zazzaɓin jini da kusan rabi kuma ya rage mutuwar masu kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi da kashi ɗaya cikin huɗu.
Ana yawan haɗa wanke hannu da sauran ayyukan kiwon lafiya a matsayin ɓangare na shirye-shiryen ruwa, tsaftacewa da tsaftacewa (WASH).
Wanke hannu yana kuma kāre mu daga cutar da ake samu ta wurin taɓa jiki.
Wani mummunar sakamako na wanke hannu shine cewa wanke hannu sau da yawa na iya haifar da rauni a fata saboda bushewar fata.
Wani bincike da aka yi a Denmark a shekara ta 2012 ya nuna cewa yawan wanke hannu zai iya sa a yi fata da kuma fushin fata da ake kira eczema ko kuma cututtukan hannu, wanda ya fi yawa a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
Ana kuma ganin yawan wanke hannu a matsayin wata alama ta cuta ta obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD).
Akwai muhimman lokuta guda biyar a rana da wanke hannu da sabulu ke da muhimmanci wajen rage yaduwar cututtuka ta hanyar bargo: bayan amfani da bayan gida (yin fitsari, bayan bayan gida), bayan share bayan yaro (canza diapers), kafin ciyar da yaro, kafin cin abinci da kafin/bayan shirya abinci ko sarrafa nama, kifi ko kaza.
Sauran yanayi da ya kamata a yi amfani da hanyoyin wanke hannu da suka dace don hana yaduwar cututtuka sun haɗa da kafin da kuma bayan kula da rauni ko rauni; bayan yin fitsari, tari ko hura hanci; bayan taɓa ƙurar dabbobi ko dabbobi; da kuma bayan taɓa shara.
A ƙasashe da yawa, ana wanke hannu da sabulu sosai.
