A ƙarshen shekarun 1990s da farkon karni na 21, masu tsabtace hannu na yau da kullun marasa ruwa da ke da tushen barasa (wanda aka fi sani da kayan tsabtace hannu na giya, kayan tsabtace hannu na antiseptic, ko tsabtace hannu) sun fara samun karbuwa.
Yawancin su ana yin su ne da isopropyl ko ethanol da aka yi da wani wakili mai kauri, kamar carbomer (polymer ko acrylic acid), a cikin gel, ko mai laushi, kamar glycerin, a cikin ruwa, ko a cikin kumfa don sauƙaƙe amfani da rage tasirin bushewar barasa.
Ƙarin hydrogen peroxide yana sa hannuwanmu su yi aiki sosai kuma masu tsabtace hannu da ke ɗauke da kashi 60 zuwa 95 cikin ɗari na giya suna kashe ƙwayoyin cuta sosai.
Masu tsabtace jiki na barasa suna kashe kwayoyin cuta, kwayoyin cuta masu jurewa (MRSA da REV), tarin fuka, da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta (ciki har da HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinoviruses, vaccia, mura da hepatitis) da fungi.
Masu tsabtace hannu da ke dauke da kashi 70% na barasa suna kashe kashi 99.97% (ragewa ta 3.5 log, kwatankwacin ragewa ta decibel 35) na kwayoyin cuta a hannaye, da dakika 30 bayan amfani da su da kuma kashi 99.99% zuwa 99.999% (ragewa ta 4 zuwa 5 log) na kwayoyin cuta a hannaye minti 1 bayan amfani da su. Masu tsabtace hannu sun fi tasiri akan kwayoyin cuta kuma basu da tasiri akan wasu ƙwayoyin cuta.
Masu tsabtace hannu da ke da barasa ba su da tasiri sosai a kan kwayar cutar norovirus (ko Norwalk), wadda ita ce sanadin cututtukan gastroenteritis. Ana iya amfani da maganin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta ko kuma masu tsabtace hannu da ke da barasa don su shafe ko kuma su rufe hannayen biyu.
Bayan haka, a shafa baya da dabino tsakanin yatsunsu da kuma ƙarshen su na kimanin dakika 30 har sai ruwan, kumfa ko gel ya bushe.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta ba da shawarar wanke hannuwanku da kayan tsabtace hannu, musamman idan hannayenku suna da datti.
Ana amfani da waɗannan magungunan da yawa saboda sauƙin amfani da saurin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta; duk da haka, bai kamata su maye gurbin wanke hannu da kyau ba, sai dai idan sabulu da ruwa ba su da yawa.
Amfani da kayan tsabtace hannu na giya sau da yawa na iya haifar da bushewar fata sai dai idan an ƙara emollients da/ko moisturizers na fata a cikin tsari.
