Ayyuka a cikin ɗakunan ajiya masu haɗari sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke cikin shirya gawawwakin mutanen da ke da tabbacin COVID-19 ko ana zargin cutar a lokacin mutuwarsu; haɗarin haɗari ya zama mai girma idan sun yi autopsy. Ƙarin sarrafa injiniya ga waɗannan rukunin haɗarin sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 ko ana zargin cutar, gami da lokacin da ake aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
