Za a yi amfani da samfurin tare da matakin 3 na biosafety.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa marasa lafiya da ke shiga asibiti su kasance a cikin yankuna biyu daban-daban na jira dangane da ko suna da cutar COVID-19. Baya ga sauran PPE, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu aikin numfashi don masu aiki a nisan ƙafa 6 daga marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar ko ake zargin suna da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da kuma masu aikin samar da aerosol.
A cikin Amurka, NIOSH-wanda aka amince da N95 masu tace ƙwayoyin cuta na fuska ko masu ɗaukar iska masu inganci ya kamata a yi amfani da su a cikin mahallin cikakken tsari da rubutaccen tsarin kariya na numfashi wanda ya haɗa da gwajin dacewa, horo da gwajin likita.
Sauran nau'ikan kayan numfashi na iya ba da kariya da haɓaka jin daɗin ma'aikaci. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da riguna ba, saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi, kuma ba a watsa ta ta ruwa na jiki ba numfashi ba.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da shawarar kawai a sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata ga ma'aikatan tantancewa a wurin shiga.
Ga masu aikin da ke karɓar samfurori na numfashi, kula ko jigilar marasa lafiya da COVID-19 ba tare da hanyoyin samar da iska ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rufe fuska, tabarau masu kariya ko kariya ta fuska, rigar tiyata da safar hannu.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, za a maye gurbin abin rufe fuska da N95 ko FFP2 respirator.
Saboda wadatar PPE a duniya ba ta isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatar PPE ta hanyar telemedicine, shinge na zahiri kamar windows mai haske, ba da damar waɗanda ke da hannu cikin kula da marasa lafiya kai tsaye su shiga ɗaki tare da mai haƙuri da COVID-19, ta amfani da PPE kawai da ake buƙata don takamaiman aikin, ci gaba da amfani da injin numfashi ɗaya ba tare da cire shi ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali ɗaya, saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da hana amfani da abin rufe fuska ga mutane marasa alamomi.
