Angiotensin mai canza enzyme nau'in 2 (ECA2) enzyme ne wanda aka haɗa a farfajiyar waje (ƙwayoyin sel) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ECA2 yana kawar da aikin enzyme mai canzawa na angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin II da haɓaka Ang (1-7), yana mai da shi magani mai ban sha'awa don magance cututtukan zuciya. ECA2 kuma yana aiki azaman hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses.
An kira ɗan adam na enzyme sau da yawa a matsayin hECA2.
Angiotensin mai canza enzyme nau'in 2 shine zinc-mai ƙunshe da enzyme wanda ke kan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin.
ECA2 yana dauke da wani yanki na N-terminal M2 peptidase da kuma wani yanki na C-terminal wanda ke dauke da amino acid da colectin a cikin tsarin koda.
ECA2 shine nau'in membrane mai wucewa guda ɗaya, tare da yankin aikin enzymatic wanda aka nuna akan farfajiyar sel a cikin huhu da sauran kyallen takarda.
Ana raba yankin ECA2 daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma ana sakin furotin mai narkewa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe a cikin fitsari.
ECA2 yana cikin gabobin da yawa: ECA2 yana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin salula na manyan ƙwayoyin alveolar huhu na nau'in II, ƙananan ƙwayoyin hanji, ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin jini da ƙwayoyin tsoka a cikin yawancin gabobin.
Ana kuma samun bayanin mRNA na ECA2 a cikin kwakwalwar kwakwalwa, jikin striatum, hypothalamus, da kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ECA2 shine ya zama mai daidaitawa ga ECA.
ASA yana raba nau'in angiotensin I zuwa nau'in angiotensin II wanda ke haifar da ƙarancin jijiyoyin jini.
ECA2 kuma yana rarraba amino acid carboxymethyl phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana haɓaka a cikin angiotensin mai fadada jini (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 kuma yana rarraba wasu peptides da yawa, gami da [des-Arg9]- bradicinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ECA2 kuma yana daidaita jigilar jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma an haɗa shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai watsawa, ECA2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin enzyme na ECA2 a farfajiyar tantanin halitta yana haifar da endocytosis da sauyawar kwayar cutar da enzyme zuwa endosomes a cikin sel.
Wannan tsarin shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar shirya furotin S ta mai masaukin serine-protease TMPRSS2, wanda hana shi yana ƙarƙashin bincike a matsayin magani mai yuwuwa. Wannan ya sa wasu suka yi tunanin cewa rage matakan ECA2 a cikin sel na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, ƙungiyoyi da hukumomin da ke kula da sana'a da yawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da tsarin hanawa na ACE da kuma maganin ARB.
Wani bita da aka yi a ranar 11 ga watan Yulin 2012 ya gano cewa "amfani da masu hana CTE yana da alaƙa da raguwar haɗarin cutar huhu da kashi 34% idan aka kwatanta da na sarrafawa".
Bugu da ƙari, "an rage haɗarin ciwon huhu a cikin marasa lafiya da ke shan ACE inhibitors waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon huhu, musamman waɗanda ke fama da bugun jini da kuma ciwon zuciya.
Amfani da ACE inhibitors kuma an haɗa shi da rage mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da cutar huhu, kodayake sakamakon bai da ƙarfi kamar na haɗarin cutar huhu gaba ɗaya".
Ana tsammanin mutum mai kwakwalwa na ECA2 (rhACE2) wani sabon magani ne don raunin huhu mai tsanani, kuma ya bayyana don inganta haemodynamics na huhu da oxygen saturation a cikin aladu tare da lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Rabin rabin rai na rhACE2 a cikin mutane shine kimanin sa'o'i 10 kuma farawa na aiki shine mintuna 30 bayan lokaci na sakamako (tsawon) na sa'o'i 24.
Yawancin binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai ban sha'awa ga waɗanda ba su da haƙuri ga masu hana tsarin renin-angiotensin na gargajiya (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma a cikin cututtukan da ke cikin jini na angiotensin II.
